### 4. Apply the LIX Formula

\[
\text{LIX} = \left(\frac{65}{3}\right) + \left(\frac{25 \times 100}{65}\right) = 21.67 + 38.46 \approx 60.13
\]

**Rounded to the nearest whole number:** **60**

---

**LIX=60**